data.description: POOL HOME WITH ALL ASSESSMENTS IN AND PAID!!! Look no further this home is looking for a new family, whether its raising your family here or a second home this enormous lanai is perfect for afternoon cocktails of outdoor meals, it was just completely re-screened in Nov 2020. This home boasts 3 bedrooms with a split floor plan with an additional family room. Real wood cabinets and stainless steel appliances. Brand new luxury vinyl flooring and 5 inch baseboards through out. Mature landscaping with new paint inside and out. AC was replaced in 2018. Come and see it because it will be gone fast!
